{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-20T07:02:00.393Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Claude can go beyond just answering questions; it can interact with tools and perform multi-step tasks."}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Tool integration"},{"type":"text","text":": Through connectors, plugins, and APIs, Claude can call external services (e.g., databases, search, APIs, cloud services) as part of its workflow."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Automated workflows"},{"type":"text","text":": It can plan and execute multi-step tasks, such as:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Fetching data from an API"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Processing it"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Generating a report"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sending it via email"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Agents"},{"type":"text","text":": In more advanced setups (especially with Claude Code or custom integrations), Claude can act as an agent that:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Monitors conditions"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Makes decisions"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Executes actions"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Learns from feedback"}]}]}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Cowork"},{"type":"text","text":" is an example of this: it’s a more productized, task-oriented experience where Claude helps you actually do work (e.g., auto-generating invoices, building marketing files, organizing business tasks) by combining language, reasoning, and tool use."}]}]}}
